ch.unibas.bsc.detapp.util

Enum GameAssets

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<GameAssets>
      • ch.unibas.bsc.detapp.util.GameAssets
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<GameAssets>

    public enum GameAssets
extends java.lang.Enum<GameAssets>
    Class to store all assets in a single place. It makes management of different assets or assets switches easier. The enum contains a AssetDescriptor which stores the assets path and type of asset.
